source.g: Zombie Food Frenzy
A Serious Game / Educational Simulation to educate on food safety and storage rules using the ABCs of safe handling
Welcome to Zombie Food Frenzy! Hungry customers await, but only safe food will keep them satisfied. Sort wisely — fridge, freezer, or pantry — and you’ll survive the lunch rush.
Drag and drop food items (Frozen brains nuggets, Cold brains salad, Brains juice, Canned brains, Brains cereal, and Frozen brains burger patties) into correct storage zones before serving.

B= Delay: Slow the growth of microorganisms by monitoring and controlling temperature. Keep cold foods below 41 °F (5 °C) and hot foods above 135 °F (57 °C). (USDA, 2025)
